OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOften dry this morning albeit
OL,6,Fwith a few showers. More frequent
OL,7,Fshowery outbreaks developing by
OL,8,Flunchtime, with the rain turning
OL,9,Fheavier and more persistent from the
OL,10,Fnorthwest later this afternoon. Mild
OL,11,Fbut windy, with winds touching gale
OL,12,Fforce in places.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FVery wet and windy this
OL,15,Fevening with clearer skies arriving
OL,16,Fovernight. Turning colder with a
OL,17,Fslight frost forming in places later
OL,18,Fand perhaps the odd wintry shower.
OL,19,FWinds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
