OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FFriday will bring a brighter
OL,6,Fbut much colder day with a mixture of
OL,7,Fcloudy periods and sunny spells.
OL,8,FPassing blustery showers are possible,
OL,9,Fthese wintry over higher ground.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,12,Ffrosty start for some on Saturday,
OL,13,Fthen bright spells and well scattered
OL,14,Fshowers. Changeable on Sunday and
OL,15,FMonday with occasional rain. Gradually
OL,16,Fturning somewhat milder, though windy
OL,17,Fat times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
